# dnd_mud project

**Stack:** Python **3.12**, console MUD, Colorama, file-based storage, pytest.

**Принцип:** простой код (`dnd-mud-python-simple.mdc`), минимум тестов (`dnd-mud-tests.mdc`).

## Commands

Из активированного `.venv` ([`01-operations.mdc`](~/.cursor/rules/01-operations.mdc) §Virtual environment):

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
make install    # venv + pip install -e ".[dev]"
make test       # pytest
make check      # ruff --fix + black + mypy
python main.py  # smoke: затронутое меню
```

